## 📖 How it Works

**For Renters:**
1. Browse the curated list of professional equipment.
2. Add your favorite gear to your personal wishlist.
3. Select your start and end dates, and book the equipment securely.
4. Check "My Bookings" to track the status of your requests.

**For Owners:**
1. Register and log in as an Equipment Owner.
2. List your professional gear by filling out the details, pricing, and uploading an image.
3. Manage your inventory seamlessly (Edit or Delete listings at any time).

## 💻 Installation

To run this project locally, clone the repo to your machine and follow these steps:

```bash
# 1. Clone the repository
git clone [https://github.com/AliAbdulla2002/Shooter-rent-equipment](https://github.com/AliAbdulla2002/Shooter-rent-equipment)

# 2. Navigate to the project folder
cd shooter-equipments

# 3. Install dependencies
npm install

# 4. Set up Environment Variables
# Create a .env file and add your PORT, MONGODB_URI, and SESSION_SECRET

# 5. Start the server
npm start


Open http://localhost:3000 in your browser.

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
